title: Lightfilled Unit at Brickyard Landing,Pt. Richmond
posting_body: ['Completely refreshed, rare ground floor 2 bedroom 2 bathroom unit with a private balcony overlooking a large garden and peek of a bay view.', 'Gleaming hardwood floors highlight the large living areas.', '2 newly carpeted separate bedroom suites feature quality built in closet organizers.', 'The master bedroom has a walk in closet.', 'Both bathrooms are tiled with a shower over the bathtub and have separate vanities.', 'There is a laundry closet filled with full sized washer and dryer.', 'The spacious, fully equipped kitchen has granite counters, stainless appliances and great cabinet space.', 'The living room boasts a cozy, wood-burning fireplace and a built in niche for displaying photos, etc.', 'A sun-filled glass enclosed atrium completes the space.', 'There are 2 parking spaces in the enclosed garage and a storage locker included.', 'The complex features a pool, gym, tennis court and a club house.', '$4000 security deposit.', '1 year lease.', '650 min.', 'credit score.', 'Income 2.5x the rent amount.', 'Renters insurance of $300K in liability along with owner listed as additional insured required.', 'For More information and viewing please call/email:', "Jana'y 510 area code 201.0214 ext.", '102', 'Janay @ <URL>', 'FMI Inc.', 'Jan Feagley, Certified Property Manager - DRE 00777442']
